OL,3,CWolves sack manager Rob Edwards after
OL,4,Cless than six months in charge
OL,6,FRob Edwards has been sacked as manager
OL,7,Fof Wolverhampton Wanderers, ITV News
OL,8,FCentral understands.
OL,10,FThe 43-year-old was appointed to the
OL,11,Frole in November 2025, following a
OL,12,Fstint at Middlesbrough.
OL,14,FEdwards will be replaced by Cesar
OL,15,FPeixoto, who manages Primeira Liga
OL,16,Fclub Gil Vicente.
OL,18,FWolves were officially relegated from
OL,19,Fthe Premier League without kicking a
OL,20,Fball in April 2026.
