OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781244253
OL,3,CWolves sack manager Rob Edwards after
OL,4,Cless than six months in charge
OL,6,FRob Edwards was brought in to try to
OL,7,Fsave the club from relegation.
OL,9,FWolves finished bottom of the Premier
OL,10,FLeague, 21 points from safety, and
OL,11,FEdwards was only able to win five of
OL,12,Fhis 30 games in charge in all
OL,13,Fcompetitions.
OL,15,FThe club made a positive start to the
OL,16,Fsummer with the signings of Kieran
OL,17,FTrippier and Raul Jimenez, while key
OL,18,Fmidfielder Andre also signed a new
OL,19,Fdeal with the club.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
