OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781244253
OL,3,CWolves sack manager Rob Edwards after
OL,4,Cless than six months in charge
OL,6,FTrippier told the club's official
OL,7,Fpodcast after signing: "I had a good
OL,8,Fchat with the manager and what struck
OL,9,Fme first was how passionate he was for
OL,10,Fhelping the club move forward to get
OL,11,Fout of the Championship next season.
OL,12,FYou just have a feeling straight away
OL,13,Fand I felt that chemistry straight
OL,14,Faway with the manager."
OL,16,FHowever, the club have now decided to
OL,17,Fmove on from Edwards, who has been
OL,18,Frelegated twice from the Premier
OL,19,FLeague after going down with Luton in
OL,20,F2024.
