OL,3,CWolves sack manager Rob Edwards after
OL,4,Cless than six months in charge
OL,6,FSpeaking after the signing of Jimenez
OL,7,Fearlier this week, Edwards was clearly
OL,8,Fstill planning for the new campaign.
OL,10,F"Hopefully they (the fans) believe
OL,11,Fmore in what we're trying to do, but
OL,12,Fthere's a lot more we've still got to
OL,13,Fdo and there'll be more to come," he
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"We know things need to improve, and
OL,17,Fwe're working really hard to try and
OL,18,Fdo that as quickly as possible. The
OL,19,Fchallenge from those above me is that
OL,20,Fwe need to get promoted again.
OL,26,@rD@AOUuD@aO]xD@AOU
