OL,3,CWolves sack manager Rob Edwards after
OL,4,Cless than six months in charge
OL,6,F"The signings we're making at the
OL,7,Fmoment will be ticking one box and
OL,8,Fthere's more to be done, but then the
OL,9,Fresults and how we start the season is
OL,10,Fwhat matters."
